snippet.title: Daggerfall: Dark Brotherhood Quest #2
snippet.description:
Another The Elder Scrolls II: Daggerfall Gameplay Video.

Assassinate a woman in the Chesterwark(a Town) Palace for The Dark Brotherhood.

Daggerfall is now FREEWARE! Bethesda Softworks have released the game as freeware on their website. http://www.elderscrolls.com/downloads/downloads_games.htm

Install instructions is also there.

The Elder Scrolls II: Daggerfall
Developer: Bethesda Softworks
Released: 1996
Genre: RPG
